{"tid":2158500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國：立即進行選舉   公民黨/民主黨：接受延任","createTime":"2020-08-15T18:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T20:04:31.000Z","uid":149857,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9518954b7c9a0c80c6f10323e0d16a216b15ea26","tid":2158500,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-ku9kLPYLzo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-ku9kLPYLzo&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=58f3e295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-ku9kLPYLzo</a> <br />\n11:20開始<br />\n<br />\n重點<br />\n<br />\n1. 杯葛立會使其失去合法性，區選已證明大多數人支持泛民。<br />\n2. 人民授權4年期限已到，臨時立會有人民授權係歪理。<br />\n3. 人大委任是非法，國際亦認同，泛民不應配合中央歪曲基本法。<br />\n4. 留守立會抗爭空間已不存在，聯合區議員成立「影子議會」議政。<br />\n5. 為下屆選舉爭取籌碼，如果下屆再DQ議員，泛民繼續杯葛。<br />\n6. 北京明顯派人放風希望泛民參加，如果泛民唔參加，等同開綠燈比美國制裁臨時立會議員、香港政府必定迎來更激烈嘅制裁。"},{"pid":"8b0fe605b53248c240b8606cd0a6a5260c778638","tid":2158500,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"點解個個討論林鄭個學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無人討論正經嘢"},{"pid":"aa55134b484bad52d1ceb6fcab158baf18d38cd7","tid":2158500,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:52:40.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"17facbaa6320736f51c445c4ad710f9182770efc","tid":2158500,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:53:33.000Z","msg":"飯民就黎傾掂數接受委任啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c078a02058ecc31dd270ccccd7f2991ad1cf2a91","tid":2158500,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"16ba3309277fe4aaf5f494b185f39fa035da6e15","tid":2158500,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"泰蟲屌你老母<img src